basics.name: Sharie Anne Mamuad
basics.label: Student
basics.summary: I am pursuing a B.S. degree in Computer Science in the Department of Information and Computer Sciences at the University of Hawaii Manoa. I expect to graduate in Spring, 2020. Afterwards, I plan to pursue my Master's degree in Computer Science.

highlights: Perform maintenance in the lab by cleaning and updating computers periodically
Assist students, faculty, and visitors of UH Manoa with their computer needs and inquiries
Troubleshoot and solve basic network and hardware problems
Provided customer service and promoted store deals and rewards program
Maintained store appeal, environment, and cleanliness throughout the shift
Provide advice and mentorship for the mentees in the 2017 summer cohort
Develop and execute an activity plan for the specific themed week of the summer program
